Rework
------

Main page
~~~~~~~~~

- button to capture photo
- button to review existing captures


Photo Capture page
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

- take photo
- show picture
- show coordinates if captured
- get coordinates--if failed
- manually fill in coordinates
- submit button(brings them to form to finish filling out)
- save for later


Existing photos
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

- list of existing photos taken
- delete button
- submit button(brings them to form to finish filling out)


Submit form
-----------

- fill in the rest of the information
- submit to server


